price: (Rabbiin) Beekaa fagooti; fagoo Isaa irratti nama tokkollee hin mul'isu.
arabic: عَٰلِمُ ٱلۡغَيۡبِ فَلَا يُظۡهِرُ عَلَىٰ غَيۡبِهِۦٓ أَحَدًا

version.title: Oromo translation
version.description: Translation of the Quran meanings into Oromo by Ghaly Ababour Abaghuna, printed in 2009.

meta.transliteration: ʿālimu al-ghaybi falā yuẓ'hiru ʿalā ghaybihi aḥadan
